              "__typename": "ParagraphTextBlock",
              "id": "about-text",
              "title": "Why We Started Verdant",
              "content": "<p>When Dr. Maya Patel left NASA's climate research division, she saw a fundamental disconnect: the science on climate change was clear, but most companies had no practical way to measure or reduce their emissions. The tools available were expensive, manual, and inaccurate.</p><p>Together with James Okafor, she built Verdant to bring the precision of climate science and the power of modern data engineering to carbon accounting. Today, our platform helps 340+ companies turn climate commitments into measurable progress.</p><p>We're backed by $62M in funding from leading climate and technology investors who share our vision of a world where every business decision accounts for its carbon impact.</p>",
